    "description": [
        "Episode of Series \"Corporation\". A close view of a wide-open management's handling of a problem with parallels far beyond the borders of Quebec. How Steinberg Ltd comes to grips with one of the major challenges it faces - the bilingual, bicultural nature of the Quebec society in which it functions - is seen, as top and middle management pursue a policy on the issues. Voice and narration by Arthur Hammond."
